⚠️ Common Mistakes

❌ Wrong folder name (views/public)
❌ Forgetting `app.set()`
❌ Mixing static & dynamic wrongly
❌ Not passing data

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

💡 Best Practices

✔ Keep static files in `/public`
✔ Keep templates in `/views`
✔ Use template engines for dynamic UI
✔ Separate frontend & backend logic

